        <updateDate>2019-03-19T19:09:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill prohibits federal agencies and nonprofit entities that conduct federally funded health care research from providing a patent for a drug based on such research until the entity receiving the patent enters into a reasonable pricing agreement with the Department of Health and Human Services.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
